        "title": "川普宣布美國成為憲法共和國，私人公司「美國公司」解散，聯邦儲備局、國稅局停業",
        "url": "https://beforeitsnews.com/politics/2026/03/byington-bombshell-report-trump-declares-us-a-constitutional-republic-no-more-privately-owned-us-inc-federal-reserve-irs-dead-3358142.html",
